    "name": "Bully Ball Brigade",
    "steam_appid": 3301400,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bully Ball Brigade is about making or breaking friendships (as any good party game). Compete in simple games, and beat your friends. <strong>Be the Best Bully there ever was.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301400/extras/98e63415875567cd3dd3968b9d3329cb.avif?t=1748462073\" width=800 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Make the game as easy or complex as you want, with </strong>roguelike<strong> spice mechanics, and full customisability.</strong> <strong>Each round's winner decides the game's pace, by choosing the next spice. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge yourselves by handpicking the available spices. Skip the spice, if the game is already overwhelming. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301400/extras/b751b3639e04617095ecbc6d91a4e9e3.avif?t=1748462073\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301400/extras_big/b751b3639e04617095ecbc6d91a4e9e3.avif?t=1748462073 width=800 height=364 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301400/extras/b3673562cd4811529f80b653c4a15a95.poster.avif?t=1748462073\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301400/extras/b3673562cd4811529f80b653c4a15a95.webm?t=1748462073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301400/extras/b3673562cd4811529f80b653c4a15a95.mp4?t=1748462073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301400/extras/a7c11d554ab134eb1fffa2657edb74be.avif?t=1748462073\" width=800 height=200 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your Big Bully stays in frame the longest, and you win! Defend from the small bullies. Easy right?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301400/extras/91bfe99b6de9513e3df6836cd306cde7.poster.avif?t=1748462073\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301400/extras/91bfe99b6de9513e3df6836cd306cde7.webm?t=1748462073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301400/extras/91bfe99b6de9513e3df6836cd306cde7.mp4?t=1748462073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301400/extras/ee8e09bc399b1005ad76d61a3b5a091e.avif?t=1748462073\" width=800 height=200 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump from gold block to gold block to evade the security guy (Big Bully). The Big Bully who catches the criminals fastest will be victorious.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301400/extras/f62b4affefa1ed515318b767059389a4.poster.avif?t=1748462073\" width=400 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301400/extras/f62b4affefa1ed515318b767059389a4.webm?t=1748462073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301400/extras/f62b4affefa1ed515318b767059389a4.mp4?t=1748462073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301400/extras/294ef16f8484d700c2cba8089c95237b.avif?t=1748462073\" width=800 height=200 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up with one of your friends (each turn a different friend). The one with the most points at the end of all turns wins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301400/extras/7ad3e2dc5df97dde42a101bea55e6bb7.poster.avif?t=1748462073\" width=400 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301400/extras/7ad3e2dc5df97dde42a101bea55e6bb7.webm?t=1748462073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301400/extras/7ad3e2dc5df97dde42a101bea55e6bb7.mp4?t=1748462073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301400/extras/9f9c59bc0721df4015462be1e47e73d6.avif?t=1748462073\" width=800 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Download, Play, and provide feedback! The demo already contains the game modes above, with spices for infinite replay-ability. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not sure if it's for you here are the requirements:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >a controller for each player</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >a cozy couch</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1-3 friends</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You don't have a couch? Try playing with Steam Remote Play Together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301400/extras/a82ad58e333e09352802eb46dc932122.avif?t=1748462073\" width=800 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If the game caught your attention, help the game development by a <strong>wishlist</strong>. <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301400/extras/295a00e3deb082f580f8a43281448b8c.avif?t=1748462073\" width=800 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you have any <strong>feedback</strong>, <strong>opinion</strong>, or <strong>ask</strong>? Reach out to me at the game's discord.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
